  --create-config {system|user|project} [PROFILE]
                              Generate a .muxmrc config file

See muxm(1) for the full option reference, profiles, and examples.
  First run: muxm --setup
  Then:      man muxm

Quick start:
  muxm --profile streaming-hevc Movie.mkv
